  Text: |-
    This example demonstrates how to use the Fetch API with the Internet Access module.
    
    Poke the cat to fetch “Cat Facts” from the internet in real time.
    Check the Animator State Manager and the Cat Fact Animator for the animation that are triggered on Poke. 
    
    Learn more about the Internet Access module here:
    https://developers.snap.com/spectacles/about-spectacles-features/apis/internet-access
